---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Barrientos Barber Studio — Barbería en Kanasín"
  description="Barbería en la Francisco Villa, Kanasín. ★ 4.5 en Google con 24 reseñas: corte, fade, barba y delineado, con clima mientras esperas tu turno. Agenda por WhatsApp."
  slug="barrientos-barber-studio"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Big+Shoulders+Display:wght@700;800&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
  favicon="💈"
  themeColor="#12181D"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529992661612"}
  telefono={"999 266 1612"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=9878163646040578960&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <!-- ============ HERO: ficha de turno ============ -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="ticket">
        <div class="pole" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="t-body">
          <p class="eyebrow">Barbería · Kanasín, Yucatán</p>
          <h1><span>Barrientos</span> <span>Barber Studio</span></h1>
          <p class="hook">
            Fade limpio, barba al ras y una sala con clima para esperar tu turno.
            Llegas, te atienden rápido y sales al cien.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/529992661612">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="19" height="19" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15L2 22l5.2-1.4A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.2c-1.6 0-3.1-.4-4.4-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-3-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2Zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1l-.8 1c-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-3.3-2.9c-.2-.4.2-.4.5-1 .1-.2 0-.4 0-.5l-.8-1.9c-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.9.9-1.1 2.2-.2 3.9a12 12 0 0 0 4.6 4.4c1.7.8 2.4.9 3.2.7.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.1-1.2-.1-.2-.3-.2-.4-.3Z"/></svg>
              Agenda por WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=9878163646040578960&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 21s-7-5.5-7-11a7 7 0 0 1 14 0c0 5.5-7 11-7 11Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2.5"/></svg>
              Cómo llegar
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="perfo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="t-stub">
          <p class="score"><span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.5 · 24 reseñas en Google</p>
          <p class="open7">Abrimos los 7 días de la semana</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ============ Cinta de oficio ============ -->
  <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="track">
      <span class="mq">CORTE · FADE · BARBA · DELINEADO · LÍNEA FRESCA · CORTE · FADE · BARBA · DELINEADO · LÍNEA FRESCA ·&nbsp;</span>
      <span class="mq">CORTE · FADE · BARBA · DELINEADO · LÍNEA FRESCA · CORTE · FADE · BARBA · DELINEADO · LÍNEA FRESCA ·&nbsp;</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ SOBRE NOSOTROS ============ -->
  <section class="sec" id="nosotros">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow-d reveal">Sobre nosotros</p>
      <h2 class="reveal">La barbería de la Francisco Villa</h2>
      <div class="prose reveal">
        <p>
          Somos Barrientos Barber Studio, en la calle 55 de la colonia Francisco
          Villa, en Kanasín. Aquí el corte no es en serie: se trabaja la línea,
          el degradado y la barba con oficio, pero sin tenerte toda la tarde en
          la silla — a nuestros clientes les gusta presumir que no nos tardamos.
        </p>
        <p>
          Y como sabemos lo que es el calor de Kanasín, la espera es con clima:
          te sientas, te relajas y cuando te toca, pasas a la silla. Buen
          ambiente y trato directo, de barbero de confianza. Abrimos los siete
          días de la semana, para que el corte caiga cuando a ti te quede.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="perks reveal">
        <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Sala de espera con clima</li>
        <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Atención rápida, sin tardanzas</li>
        <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Buen ambiente</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="perks-note reveal">— lo confirman nuestras reseñas en Google.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SERVICIOS ============ -->
  <section class="sec sec-alt" id="servicios">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow-d reveal">Servicios</p>
      <h2 class="reveal">Lo que sale de la silla</h2>
      <div class="grid-serv">
        <article class="serv reveal">
          <p class="num" aria-hidden="true">01</p>
          <h3>Corte de cabello</h3>
          <p>Clásico o moderno, con la línea marcada y el acabado parejo.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="serv reveal">
          <p class="num" aria-hidden="true">02</p>
          <h3>Fade y degradados</h3>
          <p>Del cero al punto exacto: difuminado limpio por donde lo mires.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="serv reveal">
          <p class="num" aria-hidden="true">03</p>
          <h3>Barba y bigote</h3>
          <p>Perfilado y arreglo para que el contorno quede al ras.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="serv reveal">
          <p class="num" aria-hidden="true">04</p>
          <h3>Delineado</h3>
          <p>La línea del contorno fresca, para rematar el corte.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <p class="serv-cta reveal">
        ¿Dudas de horario o disponibilidad?
        <a href="https://wa.me/529992661612">Escríbenos por WhatsApp</a> y te contestamos.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ PRUEBA SOCIAL ============ -->
  <section class="sec" id="resenas">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow-d reveal">Reseñas</p>
      <h2 class="reveal">Palabra de cliente</h2>
      <div class="score-block reveal">
        <p class="big-num">4.5</p>
        <div class="score-side">
          <p class="stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</p>
          <p class="score-sub">4.5 de 5 · 24 reseñas en Google</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews">
        <figure class="review reveal">
          <blockquote>
            <p>“Excelente lugar, el servicio es súper  top🔝, el barbero 100% recomiendado y el lugar cuenta con clima para esperar tu turno”</p>
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption><strong>Eleazar Trujeque Tello</strong> <span>· ★★★★★ · Hace 1 mes</span></figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="review reveal">
          <blockquote>
            <p>“Buen ambiente , no se tardan en hacerte el corte excelente servicio”</p>
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption><strong>Juan Montalvo</strong> <span>· ★★★★★ · Hace un año</span></figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="center reveal">
        <a class="btn btn-outline" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=9878163646040578960&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA">
          Leer más reseñas en Google
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
  <section class="sec sec-alt" id="ubicacion">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow-d reveal">Ubicación y horarios</p>
      <h2 class="reveal">Dónde nos encuentras</h2>
      <div class="loc-grid">
        <div class="loc-info reveal">
          <p class="addr">
            C. 55 444, Francisco Villa,<br />
            97370 Kanasín, Yuc., México
          </p>
          <p class="loc-tel">
            Tel: <a href="tel:+529992661612">999 266 1612</a>
          </p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=9878163646040578960&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA">
            Abrir en Google Maps
          </a>
          <div class="table-wrap">
            <table class="horas">
              <caption class="sr-only">Horarios de Barrientos Barber Studio</caption>
              <tbody>
                <tr data-day="1"><td>Lunes</td><td>10:00 – 20:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-day="2"><td>Martes</td><td>10:00 – 20:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-day="3"><td>Miércoles</td><td>10:30 – 20:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-day="4"><td>Jueves</td><td>10:00 – 20:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-day="5"><td>Viernes</td><td>9:30 – 20:30</td></tr>
                <tr data-day="6"><td>Sábado</td><td>10:00 – 20:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-day="0"><td>Domingo</td><td>8:30 – 15:18</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="map-frame reveal">
          <iframe
            title="Mapa: Barrientos Barber Studio en Kanasín"
            src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=C.+55+444,+Francisco+Villa,+97370+Kanas%C3%ADn,+Yuc.,+M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
  <footer class="foot">
    <div class="pole pole-slim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="foot-name">Barrientos Barber Studio</p>
      <p class="foot-line">Barbería · C. 55 444, Francisco Villa, Kanasín, Yuc.</p>
      <p class="foot-line">
        <a href="tel:+529992661612">999 266 1612</a> ·
        <a href="https://wa.me/529992661612">WhatsApp</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HairSalon",
    "name": "Barrientos Barber Studio",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/barrientos-barber-studio",
    "telephone": "+529992661612",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "C. 55 444, Francisco Villa",
      "addressLocality": "Kanasín",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97370",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.5",
      "reviewCount": "24"
    },
    "openingHours": [
      "Mo 10:00-20:00",
      "Tu 10:00-20:00",
      "We 10:30-20:00",
      "Th 10:00-20:00",
      "Fr 09:30-20:30",
      "Sa 10:00-20:00",
      "Su 08:30-15:18"
    ]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --bg: #12181D;
      --panel: #1B242C;
      --bone: #E8E2D4;
      --steel: #9FB3BE;
      --red: #C8442E;
      --red-hi: #E06A50;
      --pole-blue: #37505F;
      --ink: #12181D;
      --line: rgba(232, 226, 212, 0.1);
      --disp: 'Big Shoulders Display', 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
      --sans: 'Instrument Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background:
        repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(232, 226, 212, 0.028) 0 2px, transparent 2px 14px),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--bone);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: 20px; }
    .sr-only {
      position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px;
      overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0 0 0 0); white-space: nowrap; border: 0;
    }
    a:focus-visible, button:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--red-hi);
      outline-offset: 2px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* ---------- banda tipo poste de barbero ---------- */
    .pole {
      height: 10px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        var(--red) 0 12px,
        var(--bone) 12px 24px,
        var(--pole-blue) 24px 36px
      );
    }
    .pole-slim { height: 6px; }

    /* ---------- HERO: ficha de turno ---------- */
    .hero {
      padding: 48px 0 40px;
      background: radial-gradient(900px 480px at 75% -10%, rgba(200, 68, 46, 0.16), transparent 65%);
    }
    .ticket {
      --pad: 26px;
      background: var(--bone);
      color: var(--ink);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .t-body { padding: 30px var(--pad) 6px; }
    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red);
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }
    .ticket h1 {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 13vw, 4.6rem);
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .ticket h1 span { display: block; }
    .hook {
      font-size: 1.06rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: #33404A;
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      max-width: 46ch;
    }
    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 22px; }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--red);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(200, 68, 46, 0.35);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #B33A26; }
    .btn-ghost {
      border: 2px solid var(--ink);
      color: var(--ink);
      background: transparent;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(18, 24, 29, 0.07); }
    .btn-outline {
      border: 2px solid var(--bone);
      color: var(--bone);
      background: transparent;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(232, 226, 212, 0.1); }
    .btn-sm { padding: 11px 16px; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .perfo {
      position: relative;
      border-top: 2px dashed rgba(18, 24, 29, 0.35);
      margin-top: 14px;
    }
    .perfo::before,
    .perfo::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -13px;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--bg);
    }
    .perfo::before { left: -12px; }
    .perfo::after { right: -12px; }

    .t-stub {
      padding: 16px var(--pad) 18px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 6px 16px;
    }
    .score {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .score .star { color: var(--red); }
    .open7 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #5A6A76;
    }

    /* ---------- cinta ---------- */
    .marquee {
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--bone);
      border-block: 1px solid rgba(18, 24, 29, 0.25);
    }
    .track { display: flex; width: max-content; animation: mq 30s linear infinite; }
    .mq {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--ink);
      white-space: nowrap;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }
    @keyframes mq { to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

    /* ---------- secciones ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 64px 0; }
    .sec-alt { background: rgba(27, 36, 44, 0.55); border-block: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .eyebrow-d {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red-hi);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .sec h2 {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .prose p { margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--steel); max-width: 62ch; }
    .prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .perks {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 26px 0 8px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .perks li {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 9px 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .check { color: var(--red-hi); font-weight: 700; }
    .perks-note { margin: 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--steel); font-style: italic; }

    /* ---------- servicios ---------- */
    .grid-serv {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .serv {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 20px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .serv::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: 4px;
      background: var(--red);
    }
    .serv .num {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--red-hi);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .serv h3 {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .serv p { margin: 0; color: var(--steel); font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .serv-cta { margin: 26px 0 0; color: var(--steel); font-size: 0.98rem; }
    .serv-cta a { color: var(--red-hi); font-weight: 700; text-decoration-thickness: 2px; }

    /* ---------- reseñas ---------- */
    .score-block {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }
    .big-num {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 4.2rem;
      line-height: 0.9;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .stars {
      margin: 0 0 2px;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--red-hi);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red-hi) 90%, rgba(232, 226, 212, 0.22) 90%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .score-sub { margin: 0; color: var(--steel); font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .reviews { display: grid; gap: 14px; }
    .review {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 22px 18px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .review::before {
      content: "“";
      position: absolute;
      top: 2px;
      left: 16px;
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 3.4rem;
      line-height: 1;
      color: rgba(200, 68, 46, 0.4);
    }
    .review blockquote { margin: 0 0 14px; padding-left: 30px; }
    .review blockquote p { margin: 0; color: var(--bone); font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .review figcaption { padding-left: 30px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--steel); }
    .review figcaption strong { color: var(--red-hi); font-weight: 700; }
    .center { text-align: center; margin-top: 28px; }

    /* ---------- ubicación ---------- */
    .loc-grid { display: grid; gap: 24px; }
    .addr { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--bone); }
    .loc-tel { margin: 0 0 18px; color: var(--steel); }
    .loc-tel a { color: var(--bone); font-weight: 700; }
    .map-frame {
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }
    .map-frame iframe { display: block; width: 100%; height: 320px; border: 0; }

    .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; margin-top: 24px; }
    .horas {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      font-size: 0.97rem;
    }
    .horas td { padding: 10px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .horas tr:last-child td { border-bottom: 0; }
    .horas td:first-child { font-weight: 500; color: var(--bone); }
    .horas td:last-child { text-align: right; color: var(--steel); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horas tr.hoy { background: rgba(200, 68, 46, 0.14); }
    .horas tr.hoy td { color: var(--bone); }
    .horas tr.hoy td:first-child::after {
      content: " · hoy";
      color: var(--red-hi);
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    /* ---------- footer ---------- */
    .foot { margin-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 110px; text-align: center; }
    .foot .wrap { padding-top: 34px; }
    .foot-name {
      font-family: var(--disp);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .foot-line { margin: 0 0 4px; color: var(--steel); font-size: 0.92rem; }
    .foot-line a { color: var(--bone); font-weight: 600; }

    /* ---------- reveal progresivo (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- desktop ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 720px) {
      .hero { padding: 72px 0 56px; }
      .ticket { --pad: 44px; max-width: 720px; }
      .t-body { padding-top: 40px; }
      .loc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; align-items: start; }
      .map-frame iframe { height: 420px; }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    document.documentElement.classList.add('js');

    // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
    var hoy = new Date().getDay();
    var fila = document.querySelector('.horas tr[data-day="' + hoy + '"]');
    if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

    // Scroll-reveal como mejora progresiva
    if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
      var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
        entries.forEach(function (e) {
          if (e.isIntersecting) {
            e.target.classList.add('in');
            io.unobserve(e.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.12 });
      document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
    } else {
      document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
